data.description: Take a look at this beautiful home located on a Cul-d-sac. It is a 1836 sq ft 3 bedroom 2 bath home with an office that can be used as a room, a large great room and separate living room. The large master bedroom has a private bathroom with a separate tub and private toilet room with shower and a walk-in closet. The yard is big enough for setting up an al fresco in the covered patio. It has a small back yard with gated dog run on the side yard. There is also neighborhood/dog park 2 small blocks away. Panama Elementary is 4 blocks away and Ridgeview High School is in 10 minute walking distance.
